out this video on the bugs that may be in
your food.

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:26.990
Turns out, people who seem allergic to chocolate
or coffee may just be reacting to the pieces

00:03:26.990 --> 00:03:30.130
of cockroach that find their way in there
during the manufacturing process.

